sql:

    p.paper_id,
    p.title,
    p.abstract,
    p.venue,
    p.year,
    p.citation_count
FROM
    Papers p

    to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.title, '') || ' ' || coalesce(p.abstract, '')) @@ to_tsquery('english',

  p.title,
  p.abstract,
  p.venue,
  p.year,
  p.citation_count,
  ts_rank_cd(
    setweight(to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.title, '')), 'A') ||
    setweight(to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.abstract, '')), 'B'),
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'neural machine translation') ||
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'gigaword dataset') ||
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'hierarchical softmax') ||
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'importance sampling')
  ) AS relevance
FROM Papers p
WHERE
  (
    to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.title, '')) ||
    to_tsvector('english', coalesce(p.abstract, ''))
  ) @@ (
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'neural machine translation') ||
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'gigaword dataset') ||
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'hierarchical softmax') ||
    plainto_tsquery('english', 'importance sampling')
  )
ORDER BY relevance DESC
LIMIT 100
